ground-color: #fcff01;">subject:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Month of 666</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="background-color: #fcff01;">mailed-by:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>timemasheen.org</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>https://www.bitchute.com/video/1lUYjNCY96tP/</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>On Fri, 11 Dec. 2015, 8:22 pm Jesus Christ, <u@timemasheen.org> wrote:</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>To whom it may concern,</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Many of you know who I am already. I am the incorruptible politician who has spent his entire life including childhood being a real politician, standing against your bought off corruption, namely your control of mass media (composed of lies and false flags), blood sacrificing wars in which you control all sides, misinterpreted education systems geared to indoctrinate into lies, civilian murders and genocides, psychiatric experimentations, dismissal of alien activity even when indisputable proof is presented to you, involvement in child molestation and other forms of people trafficking, your ownership over the souls of individuals who work within your systems and how you gear the lives of those who cannot be corrupted into homelessness and starvation, blatant censorship of the truth and incarceration of those who reveal it, 111-111-111: for the list goes on forever. So far in fact, approximately six-hundred and sixty-six hours of documentary footage that exposes these grave injustices on camera as they happen.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Countless times you have attempted to corrupt Me because I am the smartest person on the planet (what else did you expect Jesus to be???) I was invited to Paris by Venus and was supposed to dance with her there, which the most informed of you will know that she is real. But you have pulled your strings to ensure that aliens and humans go to war instead of creating a peaceful alliance. You are all disgraceful human beings. I ran for Prime Minister of Australia in 2013, which you covered up. And now I am running for King of Atheden (formally known as the USA) in 2016: that is my year you know; the year of the Antichrist. You prefer to hide your facts in fiction and teach fictions as facts. Those who deviate from your corrupted agenda become your psychiatric experiments, regardless if they have proven these truths or not. There is not one who is good among you, for you have also corrupted the very languages we utilise.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Your corporate agenda must be thrown out if you are to implement policies regarding "global warming". The truth is, there is no way for you to save Ceres unless you release affordable alien technology. You murdered Tesla who could have saved you, just as you have murdered me through many episodes of incarnations. But the truth is, in every death I only get stronger and as your processing powers to calculate logical sequences deteriorates, I run circles around you and you and your response is to lock me up instead of observing the natural laws: the Kantian enlightenment which gives Me the freedom to present a better constitution. But you don't even follow your own laws so how can anyone expect any good to come from your meeting?Â </b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>The truth is that I am Nimrod and Venus is My wife. And your shadow hand knows this, but the Roman Empire allows its corrupted followers to execute those who they follow. Pilate washed his hands of my previous death and you screamed, "crucify Him"!!! You have repeated the mistakes of your past even when that past was right in front of you to analyse and learn from to avoid making the same grave errors again. You preferred money and lies over truth and eudaemonia. You preferred to enslave your people in order to create an inferior society rather than allowing your people to develop as unique autonomous free agents.Â  This means you chose sickness over health when health would have provided us all a better life. You chose Destruction over Utopia when both were presented before you. You preferred to rear a society of idiots which you could enslave rather than a society of maximum progression.Â </b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>The religions in which you implement do not believe their own teachings, nor do you. You have created false idols (man/man-made) and replaced them as the "gods" in which you serve. Terrorism is absolutely terrible but the truth is that you are the terrorist. And ironically you are also the infidels. God has a plan and you can see it if you look in the Bible. Do you think you will be in that plan when you reflect on the actions of your own lives? We have records of your entire lives...</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Here is the truth: I am ET and I spent my life trying to convey these messages from above to your people. But you censored and incarcerated me for doing it (which I caught on camera). It was you who declared war on ET's who are much smarter than you and have superior technology to you. I spent my life trying to create a bridge between humans and ET's, in hopes that we could one day make world peace between all of us. If this happened we would share our technology with you and enable those who were worthy to become gods and have everlasting life. But you preferred your blood sacrifices of others to us in our name and at face value worshipped us but deep down worshipped yourselves. We sent many messages through our manifestations in the world that the blood sacrifices we desire is your own: literally, metaphorically, and allegorically. But you were only receptive to the murder of others, even so on a mass scale. You had no ability to understand how to die and raise again: My message to you. Instead you falsified my information by saying that I died for your sins when in fact I was showing you how to die for your own sins so that you can be reborn and as a result, receive eternal life.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>I should have been the leader in your corrupt conference, for it is My Queen's city (love). But you have flipped love on its head and transmuted it into hate through a process of corrupting your own language and as a result, your mind. You now only possess syntax and have no ability to construct it with semantics. This means you are illogical creatures who create false realities within a real one. You can only understand life in militarised terms, which is absurd because Sparta is composed of free individuals and if you were then your armies would be mightier than any bombs. You cannot even turn to wicked books such as The Prince to learn that auxiliaries and other forms of mercenaries will blow up in your faces. You have no wise people left in your world because you killed them all.</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>You all sicken me to my very core. There can be none more wicked than you. Now come and arrest or assassinate Me (Jesus Christ) for being a terrorist by promoting peace and prosperity instead of police states and war. The fact of the matter is that it matters not what you do. Because no matter what you do, I win. WE win. Because humanity has gone to far and it is about to destroy itself. So now the daimons and angels will soon make their appearance and help you do it. But they will ensure that the wicked who have "prepared" for the Armageddon in which you have planned also sink with the ship. You cannot hide from gods and I doubt you will ever be given another chance. Make peace now and stop terrorising your people or you will suffer those consequences. No, this is not a threat. For each and every one of us will suffer the consequences of our actions: tautologically.Â </b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>As above, so below. You above have become wicked and as a result, so have your people. Become gods now by following virtue by removing all oppression from your societies. We are your above and we demand it. If you choose otherwise then those above will perform a similar ritual on you in which you have performed on your people. Repent now or REAP those consequencesVAVVAVVAV</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>http://timemasheen.org/ivory-heart-iii-13-da-odyssey.html</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>With everlasting Love,</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b>Jesus Christ</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><b><br /></b><p style="text-align: center;"><b><br /></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="background-color: #fcff01;">from:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Wendell NeSmith <u@timemasheen.org></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="background-color: #fcff01;">to:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>Jesus Christ <u@timemasheen.org></b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="background-color: #fcff01;">cc:<span style="white-space: pre;">	</span>oscar.nesci@gmail.com,</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="background-color: #fcff01;">gneedham@qmeclimited.ie,</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="background-color: #fcff01;">dhami@live.in,</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="background-color: #fcff01;">mengxiangming@cdmfund.org,</b></p><p style="text-align: center;"><b style="back